              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Solid H2 target with thickness of 100 mu-m formed on",
                "a 4.5 mu-m Ag backing foil cooled to approx. 4 K. The",
                "target cell was surrounded by a copper heat shield",
                "cooled to 28 K."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Target like reaction products were",
                "detected using a telescope consisting of 100 mu-m",
                "thick segmented silicon strip detectors and a 12mm",
                "thick CsI(Tl) array behind it. Telescope was placed",
                "12.5cm downstream of the target, covering laboratory",
                "angles of 21 deg to 46 deg."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A second dE-E telescope, consisting",
                "of 60 mu-m and 1 mm thick annular double-sided",
                "silicon strip detectors, was used to detect the",
                "beam-like He and Li nuclei. Telescope was placed 18cm",
                "from the target and covered scattering angles of 3",
                "deg to 10 deg."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Inverse kinematics was used"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 8He nuclei were produced from the spallation of a",
                "SiC target with a 500 MeV proton beam. The 8He nuclei",
                "were re-accelerated to an energy of 8.25AMeV by the",
                "superconducting linear accelerator and transported to",
                "the ISAC-II experimental hall where the IRIS facility",
                "is located."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The excitation energy of 8He was reconstructed from",
                "the measured energies and angles of the detected",
                "protons using the missing mass technique"
              ]
            }
          ],
